Source: fluidsynth-headless
Section: sound
Priority: optional
Maintainer: pistomp <pistomp@example.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), cmake,
 libasound2-dev, libdbus-1-dev, libglib2.0-dev,
 libjack-jackd2-dev | libjack-dev,
 libreadline-dev, libsndfile1-dev
Standards-Version: 4.6.2

Package: fluidsynth-headless
Architecture: arm64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Provides: libfluidsynth3
Conflicts: libfluidsynth3
Replaces: libfluidsynth3
Description: FluidSynth CLI + headless shared library
 A headless build of FluidSynth with only JACK and ALSA audio
 support (no PulseAudio, no PortAudio, no SDL3).  Ships both the
 fluidsynth CLI binary and libfluidsynth.so.3, replacing the
 Debian Trixie libfluidsynth3 package to avoid its SDL/PulseAudio
 dependencies.
